H0.text: Which whale (not James) is most commonly known as the Singing Whale. Blue Whale

H1.text: Which whale (not James) is most commonly known as the Singing Whale. Orca

H2.text: Which whale (not James) is most commonly known as the Singing Whale. Minke Whale

H3.text: Which whale (not James) is most commonly known as the Singing Whale. Humpback

A4.text: Male humpback whales produce complex songs during the winter breeding season.

A5.text: Songs have been shown in some cases to spread between neighboring populations throughout successive breeding seasons.
